<problem id="fs-idm209645232">
<para id="fs-idm177805392"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67881"/>A car dealership sells a car to a customer for $35,000. The customer makes a 10% down payment, and the dealership finances the remaining 90% in-house. How much will the car dealership record in Accounts Receivable for this customer?</para>
<list id="fs-idm209237632" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
