<para id="fs-idm223113120"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67881"/>Review the new revenue recognition guidance issued by the Financial Accounting Standards Board http://www.fasb.org/jsp/FASB/Page/ImageBridgePage&amp;cid=1176169257359 and answer the following questions.</para>
